      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an accessible entry point. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values affordability and practicality over cosmetics, but it still presents a solid opportunity for commuting, errands, or a starter vehicle. An honest, economical option with real value for the price.",
